name: Amplify
summary: Raises the user's attack.

name: Cyclone
summary: Deals damage and prevents foe from switching.

name: Dive Bomb
summary: Deals damage and briefly increases the user’s speed.

name: Dog Fight
summary: Deals ongoing damage and prevents both parties from switching.

name: Implode
summary: A huge burst of air deals massive damage to both MegaBits.

name: Pulmonate
summary: Deals a large amount of damage and lowers the foe’s defense.

name: Soar
summary: Causes brief immunity. Increases speed and attack.

name: Sonic Boom
summary: Disorients the foe, decreasing its accuracy for several turns.

name: Arc Tackle
summary: An electrically charged tackle.

name: Delete
summary: Knocks out the foe instantly.

name: Discharge
summary: Boosts the user’s crit rate at the cost of health.

name: Electrocute
summary: Damages both parties. May paralyze the foe.

name: Spark
summary: Zaps both parties with an electrical shock.

name: Static Burst
summary: Disorients the foe, decreasing speed and accuracy.

name: Thunder Smash
summary: An electrically overcharged tackle that also hurts the user.

name: Overclock
summary: The user summons up extra energy, but overheats in the process, suffering ongoing damage.

name: Blaze
summary: The user converts some health into energy.

name: Cinder Smash
summary: Bombards the foe with volcanic rock, potentially burning it.

name: Flametongue
summary: Damages the foe and applies a nasty burn.

name: Immolate
summary: Hits the foe with fire almost as hot as the surface of the sun.

name: Oxidize
summary: A small, focused burst of heat that decreases the foe's defense.

name: Rain of Fire
summary: Damages both parties, and applies a burn to the foe.

name: Scorch
summary: Singes the foe, dealing damage and lowering defense.

name: Smolder
summary: Scorching flames inflict a burn on the foe.

name: Bio Beam
summary: Massively damages the foe at the cost of the user’s health.

name: Bloom
summary: Slightly heals the user and raises its attack.

name: Ensnare
summary: Prevents foe from using any moves.

name: Evergreen
summary: Restores a small amount of health every turn.

name: Prune
summary: Damages the user to increase all other stats.

name: Root
summary: Heals the user and increases defense.

name: Sap
summary: Saps the foe's health.

name: Venom
summary: Deals damage and poisons the foe.

name: Avalanche
summary: Hits the foe with a massive wall of ice and cold air.

name: Freeze
summary: Slows the foe and deals damage when it next moves.

name: Frostbite
summary: Damages the foe and briefly lowers speed.

name: Hail
summary: Damages over time, and temporarily decreases the foe's accuracy.

name: Ice Spike
summary: Deals damage and occasionally stuns the foe.

name: Snowstorm
summary: Pelts the foe with ice. May also freeze.

name: Sublimate
summary: Surrounds the foe with fog, reducing accuracy.

name: Deep Freeze
summary: The user lowers its core temperature, decreasing its speed in order to regain energy.

name: Fracture
summary: Deals a large amount of damage.

name: Iron Defense
summary: Increases the user’s defense. May also cause immunity.

name: Quake
summary: Damages the foe and reduces accuracy.

name: Quicksand
summary: Traps the foe, reducing speed and preventing switching.

name: Refine
summary: Clears the user of any ongoing conditions.

name: Rock Wall
summary: Dramatically increases the user’s defense.

name: Splinter
summary: Shards of rock damage the foe over time.

name: Cataclysm
summary: An enormous rift in the earth opens — both the user and the foe suffer ongoing damage.

name: Alternate
summary: Forces the foe to switch, if possible.

name: Drain
summary: Drains the foes health and energy.

name: Evil Eye
summary: The foe becomes uneasy and loses energy.

name: Funeral Pyre
summary: An eruption of spiritual fire knocks out both parties.

name: Hex
summary: Reduces the foe’s health and energy over time.

name: Hypnotize
summary: Puts the foe to sleep.

name: Omen
summary: Increases the user's crit rate for several turns.

name: Soulfire
summary: Sharply increases the energy regained for several turns.

name: Bite
summary: A swift attack with sharp teeth.

name: Focus
summary: Increases the user's crit rate briefly.

name: Fury
summary: Increases the user's crit rate and attack.

name: Headbutt
summary: A solid headbutt. May stun the foe.

name: Rebuild
summary: Resets the user’s health and energy.

name: Shuffle
summary: The Ali shuffle. Increases speed and accuracy.

name: Stutter Punch
summary: Delivers damaging punches over several turns.

name: Sucker Punch
summary: If the foe has full health, this move will crit.

name: Swift Kick
summary: A simple kick.

name: Cleanse
summary: Removes all conditions from both parties.

name: Dunk
summary: Causes brief immunity for the foe, but also stuns.

name: Flood
summary: Submerges the foe in an unavoidable deluge of water.

name: Gel
summary: Decreases the foe’ speed with a viscous fluid.

name: Plunge
summary: Causes brief immunity. Increases speed and accuracy.

name: Riptide
summary: Forces the foe to switch, if possible.

name: Squirt Gun
summary: A high-pressure burst of water that deals consistent damage.

name: Torrent
summary: Strikes the foe with repeated blasts of water.

name: Undertow
summary: A massive current sweeps the foe away, knocking it out instantly.
